        "excerpt":"ğŸ’¡ Introduction   Managing expenses shouldnâ€™t feel like managing a spreadsheet. Thatâ€™s what drove the idea behind Smart Expense Manager â€” a conversational, intelligent solution for personal and group expense tracking, built using Telegram, Razorpay, Gemini AI, and MongoDB.   This was my hackathon entry for a software innovation challenge â€” and it turned into one of the most fun and useful projects Iâ€™ve built!     ğŸ§  What the System Does      â€œA Telegram message is all it takes.â€    This smart assistant helps users:     ğŸ“¥ Log expenses easily from chat   ğŸ‘¥ Split bills with friends in real-time   ğŸ¤– Use AI to suggest budgets based on spending   ğŸ’° Handle payments using Razorpay   ğŸ“² Get alerts via SMS   All without ever leaving Telegram.     ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack                  Layer       Stack Used                       Frontend       Telegram Chat UI                 Backend       Node.js + Express                 AI Engine       Gemini API (Google AI)                 Database       MongoDB Atlas                 Payments       Razorpay Integration                 Alerts       Twilio SMS / Bot API             ğŸ§± Architecture Overview      User sends command to the Telegram bot (/add, /split, /view, /suggest)   Bot sends the data to a Node.js backend   User data, group metadata, and expenses are stored in MongoDB   The backend:            Calls Gemini AI to suggest budgeting categories and limits       Calls Razorpay API to send payment links if needed       Sends SMS reminders through Twilio           User receives updates â€” budget suggestions, summaries, and payment confirmations â€” right inside Telegram.     ğŸ”‘ Core Features   1. ğŸ’¬ Telegram Chat Bot     Intuitive chat-first interface   Expense logging in seconds   Group creation &amp; invite support   2. ğŸ§  Gemini AI Budgeting     Analyzes past spend data   Recommends monthly budget goals   Adjusts based on user behavior   3. ğŸ’¸ Razorpay Integration     Real-time request-to-pay system   Pings payer via UPI or card   Confirms payments instantly   4. ğŸ“¢ Alerts via SMS / Telegram     Sends transaction confirmations   Daily/weekly budget digests   Payment reminders     ğŸ’¼ Example Use Case   You enter: ```bash /split Pizza 1200 with @rohan @raj @meena â¡ï¸ The bot:   Splits amount â‚¹300 each   Sends Razorpay requests   Logs in MongoDB   Notifies users via SMS + bot chat   ğŸ”® Future Scope Voice-command support with Google Assistant   Expense forecasting with ML   Integration with bank APIs   Android/iOS native companion app   Leaderboard of budgeters (gamification)   âœ¨ Takeaway This project helped me explore:   Real-time APIs and integrations   Multi-user concurrency via chatbots   Payment flow design   AI-in-the-loop systems   Itâ€™s the perfect example of how GenAI + full-stack dev can create delightful user experiences â€” that are actually useful.   ","categories": ["full-stack"],
